game.name: Frozen Sisters Facebook Fashion
game.description:
The frozen sisters have got the invitation for the Taylor Swift Concert from Elsa. It is a big Facebook concert where they look pretty excited to get participated. But, the problem is that they do not have enough knowledge what to wear for this big event. Will you give the frozen sisters a favor by helping them to shop for the right outfits? Join Frozen Sisters Facebook Fashion game and assist these two beautiful princesses to make a decision for the right outfits!
This concert is very big, so their preparation is. Take them to the mall and help them decide to purchase some cool

Outfits for the concert that will take place tonight! Trying out this brand new dressing game will allow you to enter a new type of world where your utmost designer abilities will surely work out! Get them ready for the concert and see them wearing the crown of a big event! The final victory will help them to realize their dream in this one of the best girls games! 
Choose the girl you want to go for shopping with first! Then select a mall and explore all the outfit options available there.

Allow them to pick out a perfect hairstyle, a pair of matching shoes, handbags while entering the mall you see on the left side of the screen. The outlet available at the ride side of the screen will take you to a wide array of outfits, including shorts, frock style dresses, multiple colored tops, full-length gown, and a lot more. Remember you will have a limited budget for every shopping so be careful while buying any product for your princess. Good luck to have a blast online, no download required!!
